768px <   					:   xs
768px >= & < 992px  :		sm
992px >= & < 1200px :		md
>= 1200px 					:		lg


screen	|	num of Blocks	 |	Cols/block	|		Formula	
--------+----------------+--------------+--------------
lg 			| 			4 			 |			3				|		col-lg-3
md 			|				3				 |			4 			|		col-md-4			 
